title: Rare 1993 Macintosh TV Exploration (and Logic Board Swap) - Krazy Ken's Tech Misadventures
tags: Rare 1993 Macintosh TV Exploration (and Logic Board Swap)
description: The 1993 Macintosh TV is quite rare. Apple sold it for only 4 months. Today, Krazy Ken explores the hardware and hard disk contents of this computer. In addition, he performs a logic board swap to save this computer and the world.  Support the show and get in the credits   Want more videos like this?   Subscribe for more tech videos!   Watch part 2    Like the CC on Facebook   Follow the CC on Twitter   Follow Ken on Twitter: @Hildron101010  Krazy Ken's Tech Misadventures #81 - Rare 1993 Macintosh TV Exploration (and Logic Board Swap)  Krazy Ken is now on Patreon! Pledge now to help support the show and get an opportunity to be in the show's credits!   Contact the CC    Want music for your videos?   (We use these guys a lot. They're good.)
